### =========================
### 🌐 BASE URL
### =========================
@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:5000/api

### =========================
### 🔐 1. SIGNUP
### =========================
### Test API
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### =========================
### 🔐 2. LOGIN (COPY TOKEN)
###
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "sukanya_kake@gmail.com",
  "password": "1"
}

### =========================
### 🔑 SET TOKEN HERE AFTER LOGIN
### =========================
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### =========================
### 🔥 3. SYNC DATA
### =========================
POST {{baseUrl}}/datasources/sync
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "signals": {
    "screen_time": 5,
    "unlocks": 80,
    "steps": 5100,
    "sleep": 7
  }
}

### =========================
### 📜 4. RAW LOGS
### =========================
GET {{baseUrl}}/datasources/raw_logs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### =========================
### 📊 5. SYNC SUMMARY
### =========================
GET {{baseUrl}}/datasources/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### =========================
### 📊 6. DASHBOARD
### =========================
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### =========================
### 📈 7. BEHAVIOUR
### =========================
GET {{baseUrl}}/behaviour/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### =========================
### 🤖 8. PREDICTION
### =========================
GET {{baseUrl}}/prediction/forecast
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### =========================
### ✨ 9. ACTION CENTER
### =========================
GET {{baseUrl}}/action/plan
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}